#🚀 FocusFlow
🤖 AI That Protects Your Deep Work

FocusFlow is an AI-powered productivity web app that intelligently filters developer interruptions and protects deep work sessions. It analyzes notifications, classifies urgency, and blocks non-essential distractions when Focus Mode is enabled.

#✨ Features

🧠 Smart urgency classification (keyword scoring)
🔐 Focus Mode to block non-urgent notifications
📊 Real-time productivity dashboard
🎯 Dynamic Focus Score calculation
🔄 Developer interruption simulation
🌙 Modern glassmorphism SaaS UI
📱 Fully responsive design


#🛠 Tech Stack
HTML
CSS
Vanilla JavaScript

Lightweight. Fast. Framework-free.


#📊 Focus Score Formula
Focus Score = (Blocked / Total) × 100


